-- Clínica Dental Raslan - English-speaking dental clinic in Barcelona
('Clínica Dental Raslan', 'Dental', 'English-speaking family dental clinic in Barcelona with a multidisciplinary team of highly trained dentists. Led by Dr. Fady Raslan, the only specialist in Barcelona accredited in Advanced Prosthodontics in both Europe and the USA by Boston University Henry M. Goldman School of Dental Medicine. The clinic offers the most advanced treatments in dental implantology, orthodontics, and dental aesthetics using cutting-edge 3D technology. Services include: dental implants (including short implants, immediate load, and full denture rehabilitation), orthodontics (Invisalign certified center for invisible orthodontics), dental aesthetics (veneers and teeth whitening), endodontics (microscopic and 3D-planned microsurgery), periodontics (gum disease treatment including gingivitis, periodontitis, and peri-implantitis), prosthodontics (fixed and removable dentures), preventive dentistry, and odontopediatrics. Two convenient locations in Barcelona: Sarrià – Sant Gervasi area and Eixample (Plaza Tetuán). 24-hour emergency dental service available 365 days a year including weekends, with same-day appointments. Offers tailored financing plans, accepts international insurances, and provides gift cards. First visit free. English-speaking staff including US-trained dentists.', 'C/Ganduxer 59 Bis, Barcelona (also Pl. Tetuán, 16, 08010 Barcelona for 24h emergencies)', 'Barcelona', 'Barcelona', '+34 937 656 788 / +34 669 154 020', 'info@clinicaraslan.com', 'https://clinicaraslan.com/en/', true, false, true, false, NOW(), NOW());
